<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idef75bcf1-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s2209g"><num value="2209g">§ 2209g.</num><heading> Availability of funds for uniforms or allowances</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">On and after <date date="2005-11-10">November 10, 2005</date>, funds appropriated by this or any other Appropriations Act to the Department of Agriculture (excluding the Forest Service) shall be available for uniforms or allowances as authorized by law (<ref href="/us/usc/t5/s5901–590">5 U.S.C. 5901–590</ref>2).</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idef75bcf2-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/109/97/tVII/s702">Pub. L. 109–97, title VII, § 702</ref>, <date date="2005-11-10">Nov. 10, 2005</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/119/2149">119 Stat. 2149</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
